work with Uruguayan writers,"

00:06:24.240 --> 00:06:27.140
and then as it turns out, we
have a mutual friend and we ended

00:06:27.140 --> 00:06:28.600
up having lunch together.

00:06:28.600 --> 00:06:31.280
And at the time, Jesse was,
Jesse Lee was really working

00:06:31.280 --> 00:06:35.870
on her translations of Circe Maia,
and she, after the conference,

00:06:35.870 --> 00:06:39.360
