that was different,

00:08:27.750 --> 00:08:30.910
and that's that trans
word for translation.

00:08:30.910 --> 00:08:32.500
You're carried somewhere else.

00:08:32.500 --> 00:08:36.200
So Jesse Lee's skill
and her subtlety

00:08:36.200 --> 00:08:39.430
as a translator really
brought through what we strive

00:08:39.430 --> 00:08:42.010
for in translation -- to
capture the voice of somebody.

00:08:42.010 --> 00:08:46.320
And I'm really excited that you're
going to hear that voice tonight.

00:08:46.320 --> 00:08:51.910
